## North star ‚Äî Workers must work in iPix apps

Unit / Worker vitest green is **necessary but not sufficient**.

**Primary success criterion:** a real iPix persona completes a journey that hits the AI Gateway Worker and gets a correct, usable result in the product UI (or typed API the UI uses).

| Priority | Proof | Example |
|----------|-------|---------|
| **1 ‚Äî Journey** | Operator / marketing / BI / embed path through app ‚Üí Worker | `UJ-OP-CHAT`, `UJ-MKT-CHAT`, `UJ-EMBED` |
| **2 ‚Äî Local Runtime** | `wrangler dev` + curls matching the journey‚Äôs Worker route | Chat stream + embed 768-d |
| **3 ‚Äî Unit** | Worker + adapter vitest | Allowlist, envelopes, dims |

Do **not** claim gateway / AC-F / AC-J Done on unit tests alone. Name journey IDs from the reference doc in the PR test plan.

