## Risk tier (pick one before coding)

| Tier | When | Minimum verify |
|------|------|----------------|
| **A ‚Äî Thread / unit** | Clear review nit, pure Worker unit logic, no deploy config | Focused vitest + typecheck on touched package |
| **B ‚Äî Gateway / Worker** | `services/cloudflare-worker/**`, embed/error contracts, provider adapter | Worker tests + **at least one matching journey** (or documented curl stand-in for UJ-EMBED) at Local Runtime |
| **C ‚Äî Platform / AC-F / AC-J** | `resolveModel`‚Üígateway, streaming, OpenNext, bindings, deploy | Build as needed + **UJ-HEALTH + UJ-OP-CHAT + UJ-MKT-CHAT** (+ UJ-EMBED if embed touched); Remote Preview when available |

Escalate if confidence &lt; 80%, or auth / secrets / production traffic is involved.

