## CF-only deltas (on top of `task-accuracy`)

### 0. Orient (Tier B/C)

```bash
graphify query "<Worker|AI Gateway|OpenNext|bindings>"
gh pr list --state open --search "cloudflare OR gateway OR wrangler"
```

Duplicate open PR / Linear issue ‚Üí stop and redirect.

### Docs before API claims

For Workers runtime, bindings, Workers AI, AI Gateway, OpenNext:

1. Cloudflare docs MCP (`search_cloudflare_documentation`) **or** hub `references/`
2. Installed package / types if disputed
3. Then code

Never assert `node:fs` support/limits from memory ‚Äî check `nodejs_compat` + `compatibility_date` + docs.

### `node:fs` (Workers)

- Virtual bundled FS with `nodejs_compat` ‚Äî **not** arbitrary disk.
- Safe: static `import` / bundled assets.
- Unsafe: runtime `readFileSync(userPath)` expecting real disk.

### Verification level (always name one)

| Level | Meaning |
|-------|---------|
| Unit Verified | Tests only |
| Build Verified | `next build` / Worker build |
| Local Runtime Verified | `wrangler dev` / local preview |
| Remote Preview Verified | `*.workers.dev` or CF preview URL |
| Production Verified | Live prod smoke |

Never say bare ‚ÄúVerified.‚Äù Never claim Production without prod evidence.

### Right-size Stage 4/5

1. Targeted tests first (seconds).
2. Pre-push already runs app typecheck + vitest ‚Äî don‚Äôt re-litigate unless CF package isn‚Äôt covered.
3. Full OpenNext build ‚Äî **required** when touching `open-next.config.*`, `wrangler.*`, bundling deps; else CI `app-build` may suffice for ordinary app code.
4. `wrangler deploy --dry-run` ‚Äî cheap config/binding sanity.
5. Prefer platform safety nets when available (Workers Builds preview, gradual deploy, `wrangler rollback`) over exhaustive local prophecy ‚Äî see ENGINEERING-WORKFLOW ‚ÄúRight-sizing verification.‚Äù

### Bundle audit (Tier C / OpenNext only)

After `opennextjs-cloudflare build`:

- `.open-next/worker.js` + `assets/` exist
- No secrets: `SERVICE_ROLE`, `GEMINI_API_KEY`, `GROQ_API_KEY`, etc.
- Investigate unexpected `require(`, `readFileSync`, `eval(`, `Function(`

### Docs / Linear contradiction

Before Done: Source == Tests == Runtime == PR/docs == Linear.  
Mitigations ‚âÝ complete fixes ‚Äî label honestly.

