## Outcome Grader (merge gate)

| Criterion | Pass |
|-----------|------|
| **iPix journey proof (Tier B/C)** | Named `UJ-*` from `worker-user-journeys.md` run (or explicit waiver) |
| Official docs checked for runtime API claims | MCP / hub refs used |
| Verify level named honestly | Matches what was actually run |
| Scope / one concern | No docs+code mix; no sibling task |
| Regression test on bug fixes | Fails before, passes after |
| Embed/error contract (if touched) | Contract rows + **UJ-EMBED** |
| Bundle audit (if OpenNext touched) | No secrets / no surprise Node |
| Linear / PR body | Match reality; journey IDs in test plan |

Any Fail = blocker unless explicitly waived with reason in the PR.

